data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. NEW PRICE! ATTENTION HOME BUYERS! BOATERS! FISHERMAN! LOCATION LOCATION LOCATION! One-of-a-kind home with amazing water views and amazing fishing! Premium oversized lot only 1 block away from Tampa Bay! No bridges, deep water, ideal for large power boat or sailboat! This home offers an amazing open floor plan and plenty of windows allowing natural light into your living spaces. The kitchen / Livingroom combination opens up to the oversized Lanai featuring multiple places for sitting, lounging, dining areas and of course the pool overlooking wide-open water view, where you can appreciate Dolphin, Manatees, fish and wildlife... perfect for entertaining and making memories! You will find the master bedroom downstairs. with its own on suite bathroom. On the second floor you will find spacious bedrooms and water views from every room.   There is also an observatory tower for those wanting a quiet and relaxing private place for storm and sunset watching or simply sip on your favorite beverage. The covered dock has both a boat and jet ski lift.
